             was brought into the Room, in a large black Coat, big enough to hold 2 or 3 of him, he being but a slender Man, and a very large Hat on his Head. That this Charles, Motherby took upon himself to be the Thief, and produc'd the Bag wherein the Things had been stolen, and 19 Rings, 2 Gold Chains, and a Silver Watch. That these Things being produc'd, the 6 Guineas were laid down upon the Table, and taken up by 
               <persName id="t17221205-43-person299">
                  John 
                  Hornby 
