            , he talk'd sharply to him, threatning him, that if he did not confess the Truth he should be sent to Newgate. That then Mothorby begg'd for Favour, and said he was a Perriwig-maker in Golden Lane, and that the Person who stole the Goods was one 
               <persName id="t17221205-43-person302">
